title: Checkbox List
---

p.-text
  | Checkbox lists are used to wrap a series of checkbox on a list.

h3 Examples
h4 Base
p.-text To render a series of checkbox in a list, apply the class <code>m-listGroup</code> in a list.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    h5 Select an option
    ul.m-listGroup(style="max-width:20rem")
      li.m-formGroup
        input(type="checkbox", class="a-input", id="checkbox1")
        label(for="checkbox1")
        label.-text(for="checkbox1") Option 1
      li.m-formGroup
        input(type="checkbox", class="a-input", id="checkbox2")
        label(for="checkbox2")
        label.-text(for="checkbox2") Option 2
      li.m-formGroup
        input(type="checkbox", class="a-input", id="checkbox3")
        label(for="checkbox3")
        label.-text(for="checkbox3") Option 3
      li.m-formGroup
        input(type="checkbox", class="a-input", id="checkbox4")
        label(for="checkbox4")
        label.-text(for="checkbox4") Option 4
      li.m-formGroup
        input(type="checkbox", class="a-input", id="checkbox5")
        label(for="checkbox5")
        label.-text(for="checkbox5") Option 5
